'''List of Fellows of the American Academy in Rome''' is a list of those who have been awarded the [[Rome Prize]]. The Rome Prize is a prestigious American award made annually by the [[American Academy in Rome]], through a national competition, to 15 emerging artists (working in Architecture, Landscape Architecture, Design, Historic Preservation and Conservation, Literature, Musical Composition, or Visual Arts) and to 15 scholars (working in Ancient, Medieval, Renaissance and early Modern, or Modern Italian Studies).<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sof-aarome.org/sof_directories.html |title=Directory by Year Index |publisher=Society of Fellows of the American Academy in Rome |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080416233433/http://www.sof-aarome.org/sof_directories.html |archive-date=April 16, 2008 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>
